&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own &lt;strong&gt;600+ target accounts&lt;/strong&gt;, proactively engaging with &lt;strong&gt;Director+ level buyers&lt;/strong&gt; in Sales, Marketing, and RevOps.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive &lt;strong&gt;90% outbound new business&lt;/strong&gt;, creating &lt;strong&gt;3x pipeline coverage&lt;/strong&gt; to exceed quota.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Run &lt;strong&gt;4+ strategic meetings per day (20+ per week)&lt;/strong&gt; across &lt;strong&gt;discovery, demos, and closing conversations&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
