&lt;p&gt;The Billing Advocate position is open to residents of Mexico City and requires full English fluency.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://Apollo.io&quot;&gt;Apollo.io&lt;/a&gt; is seeking a Billing Advocate to join our Customer Support team. In this role, you will be the primary point of contact for billing-related inquiries — handling refunds, cancellations, subscription renewals, invoice discrepancies, and payment questions, while adhering to established workflows and company policies.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your attention to detail, billing system proficiency, and commitment to customer satisfaction will be critical to maintaining trust and accuracy in Apollo&#39;s financial operations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an IC role reporting to the &lt;strong&gt;Account Advocate Team Lead&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
