&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re hiring a &lt;strong&gt;Lead PMM, Narrative &amp;amp; Content&lt;/strong&gt; to own that gap. This is a true PMM + content hybrid: you&#39;ll work with Apollo’s exec team to build narratives that break through the noise to position Apollo as the default AI native system for GTM teams. You’ll also own operationalizing that narrative by owning the content strategy that gets this narrative into market - long form research based content, exec thought leadership, and proof points that shift how the market sees us. You&#39;ll work shoulder-to-shoulder with our CEO, CRO, CMO, and product PMMs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a senior IC role for an experienced product marketer who&#39;s just as comfortable writing the LinkedIn post as building the messaging house behind it. If you&#39;ve ever been the person quietly translating an exec&#39;s half-formed idea into the narrative everyone ends up repeating — this role is built for you.&lt;/p&gt;
