&lt;p&gt;This role owns &lt;strong&gt;Deliverability &amp;amp; Connectivity&lt;/strong&gt;, the trust layer that determines whether Apollo can reliably send, sync, route, suppress, enrich, and activate across a customer’s GTM stack.&lt;/p&gt;
